{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821800/extras/DrillCore_Needs_You600.png?t=1734079279\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Join Our Elite Platform Manager Team at DrillCore!</h2><br>Are you ready to lead a team of exceptional talent in one of the most challenging environments known to humankind?<strong> At DrillCore, we're not just mining minerals; we're safeguarding the future.</strong> We're looking for strategic minds and resourceful leaders to manage our cutting-edge operations. Do you have what it takes to make every decision count in the race <span class=\"bb_strike\">to profits &amp; earnings</span> against climate collapse?<br><br><strong>Your 'Exciting' Mission: Lead, Manage, Innovate</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821800/extras/DC_Drill_Platform_1.gif?t=1734079279\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strategic Leadership</h2><br>As a Platform Manager at DrillCore, you'll oversee a dedicated team of miners, carriers, and guards. Your mission? Navigate them through perilous missions to extract vital minerals and power our drill platform. <strong>Every strategic decision will test your planning and resource management skills.</strong> You\u2019ll report directly to your Sector Manager, he will make sure you keep the operation running smoothly, whatever the pressure you\u2019re under.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821800/extras/DC_Turrets.gif?t=1734079279\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Operational &amp; Safety Excellence</h2><br><strong>Nighttime is when the real excitement begins.</strong> This is when the planet's fauna usually clash directly with our company\u2019s safety commitments. Your job? To maintain profits while safeguarding both the lives of your crew and the biodiversity of the planet you\u2019re drilling. Sometimes tough choices need to be made, and that\u2019s why <strong>DrillCore equips you with state-of-the-art defensive turrets</strong>. Remember,<strong> it's NOT a crime against biodiversity if it\u2019s self-defense.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821800/extras/DC_Green_Turrets.gif?t=1734079279\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Innovation and Adaptability</h2><br><strong>At DrillCore, no two challenges are the same.</strong> Unpredictable wildlife, evolving requirements, and ever-changing technologies will keep you on your toes. Adapt swiftly, allocate resources efficiently, and develop innovative strategies to overcome the unexpected. Your success unlocks new career opportunities and advancements, pushing the boundaries of what's possible.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821800/extras/SteamPage_Recruitmentpoints600px.png?t=1734079279\" /><br><br>Join us at DrillCore and become a part of a mission that matters. Apply your strategic mind, lead with confidence, and make a real impact. <strong>Are you ready to drill to the core?</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Drill Core","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2821800/b99d8c2a5094226dc5138f1c46432b950cf78dec.jpg"},{"name":"You're Cold as Ice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2821800/c2b767f28e60bcd83d5b6f90e4e071a3c824509f.jpg"},{"name":"Passed Probation Period","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2821800/9447853bfaf92ca157e85f8f863ce23b75f2418d.jpg"},{"name":"Professional Manager","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2821800/8bd88d2a5f191eed63bafa27f649e2cad8ebe85c.jpg"},{"name":"Company Leading Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2821800/e2189c380caaf60cc5ce68a1f15b003d1e